\id 2TI 2 Timothy in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08 
\h 2 Timↄtee 
\toc1 Timↄtee lá plaade 
\toc2 2 Timↄtee 
\toc3 2Tim 
\mt1 TIMƆTEE LÁ PLAADE 
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ 
\ip Pↄlu lá plaadepi kɛ̃̀ Timↄteeɛ za Lomaɛ (1.17). Wà wɛtɛ̃amↄ̀ Pↄluɛ we pãsĩpãsĩ (2.9), a ku yooyea (4.10, 16). À kà a zĩ láaa (4.6), ↄ̃ àlɛ lɛda a ìwa yenzidewa (1.2). 
\ip À nà Lua sáaukpaawa Timↄtee yeanzi ń aà luanaaikɛao yã́ musu. Wɛtɛ̃a ń taasio ń íbɛlɛ pↄ́ wì sɛ́ ń baonakpanaↄ yã́i à lɛdà Timↄteewa aà zɛ gbãa, aà taasikɛanↄ Kilisi zĩgↄ̃ maa ũ (1.3-2.13). A òɛ̀ aà mikɛ̃ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaìↄ gbɛ̃́ↄ lɛwɛↄ yã́wa, asa aaìↄ yãkpaanlaↄ lɛkpaakɛkɛ ń gbɛ̃́ↄɛ, ↄ̃ aaì n luanaaikɛa ↄ̃̀ↄkpa. A òɛ̀ aà a ↄlɛsɛ, aà zɛ ń Lua yã́ pↄ́ a dàda za a ɛ̀waasogↄↄo (2.14-4.5). Lápi láakĩi Pↄlu azĩa yã́ↄ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ɛ̀, lá a ku ga lɛ́zĩ Loma, ãma a dↄ̃ kɛ́ Lua a a suaba e a gɛ kaò aà kpalau musu. 
\ip Pↄlu dɛ̃ɛ maa nɛ̀ à baonakpà e a lɛ́wa (4.7), ↄ̃ à tɛkpà lápi kyokɛnaↄgu aa dɛ̃ɛ doũpi ká ń luanaaikɛao ń mɛnao ń yeańzio vĩakɛa ibɛɛↄnɛ sai. 
\c 1  
\s1 Pↄlu tɛ́kpaa Timↄteegu 
\p  
\v 1 Mámɛmaa Kilisi Yesu zĩna Pↄlu lá Lua yeiwa wɛ̃ni pↄ́ à a lɛgbɛ̃̀ Kilisi Yesupi guu yã́i,  
\v 2 ma láɛ bee kɛ̃̀nɛ, ma nɛ́ yenzide Timↄtee.\f + \fr 1.2 \ft Zĩn 16.1\f* Mae Lua ń wá Dii Kilisi Yesuo gbɛ̃kɛkɛnɛ ń sùuuo, aai n gba aafia. 
\p  
\v 3 Ma sáaukɛ̀ ń ma deziↄ Lua pↄ́ mi kúlɛɛ̀ ń nↄ̀sɛpuaoo, asa n yã́ ìↄ dↄmagu láasai ma wabikɛa gwãasĩna ń fãanɛo guu.  
\v 4 Tó wɛ́'i pↄ́ bↄ̀ma yã́ dↄ̀magu, mi n bɛɛkɛɛ, míↄ ye wà wɛsikↄ̃lɛ, kɛ́ ma pↄna e kɛ zài.  
\v 5 N luanaaikɛa ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo ìↄ dↄmaguɛ. N dazi Loisi ń n da Ɛnisio Lua náaikɛ̀ màa, mɛ́ má dↄ̃ sã́asã ńlɛ Lua náaikɛ màa sↄ̃. 
\p  
\v 6 Ayãmɛto málɛ dↄngu, fɛlɛ zɛ ń gba pↄ́ Lua dànɛ gↄↄ pↄ́ ma ↄnàmao,  
\v 7 asa Nisĩna pↄ́ ì wá gba gbãa, ì to wàↄ yekↄ̃i, ì to wàↄ laai vĩ ↄ̃ Lua kpàwá, i kɛ nisĩn fooo no.  
\v 8 A yã́i ńsu widɛ ń wá Dii yã'oanɛ́oo, mɛ́ ńsu widɛ ma gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wà ma dakpɛu aà yã́i yã́ musuo. Taasi pↄ́ wì kɛ aà baokpaa yã́i kɛmanↄ ń Lua gbãao.  
\v 9 Ɔ̃mɛ wá suabà, à wá sisi, wa gↄ̃ aà pↄ́ ũ. I kɛ yã́ pↄ́ wá kɛ̀ yã́i no, aàzĩa pↄeã yã́iɛ, ń gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ a kɛ̀wɛ̃ɛ naa Kilisi Yesuwa zadↄ̃ gↄↄ i daalɛoo.  
\v 10 Gbɛ̃kɛpi bↄ̀ gupuau wá Suabana Kilisi Yesupi mↄa guu sa. À ga iko bãdɛ̀, à wɛ̃ni ń kua gↄↄpiio bↄ̀wɛ̃ɛ gupuau a bao pↄ́ wì kpa guu.  
\v 11 Lua ma dilɛ a zĩna ũ mà baopi kpàwakɛ, mí danɛ́.\f + \fr 1.11 \ft 1Tim 2.7\f* 
\v 12 A yã́i málɛ taasiɛ bee kɛi, ãma wí lí ma kũo, asa má gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ma aà náaikɛ̀ dↄ̃, mɛ́ má dↄ̃ sã́asã kɛ́ a fↄ̃ kàeda yã́ pↄ́ à nàmɛɛ ma ↄzĩi e a mↄgↄↄzĩ.  
\v 13 Ǹyↄ̃ yã́ sĩande pↄ́ ń mà ma kĩ́ipi kũa yã́ zĩ́nda ũ ń luanaaikɛao ń yeakↄ̃io naa Kilisi Yesuwa guu.  
\v 14 Kàeda yãmaa pↄ́ Lua nànɛ n ↄzĩi ń aà Nisĩna pↄ́ kú wá guu gbãao. 
\p  
\v 15 Ń dↄ̃ kɛ́ Azi bùsudeↄ píi ma vũaaɛ. Fizɛlɛ ń Ɛɛmↄzɛnio kú ń guu.  
\v 16 Dii wɛ̃nadↄ̃ Ɔnɛsifↄↄ bɛdeↄnɛ! Asa à ma nↄ̀sɛ nìnimɛɛ, a gɛ̃na lɛ́ vĩo, i widɛ ma daakpɛu yã́ musuo.  
\v 17 Kɛ́ à kà Loma gↄ̃̀ↄ, à ma wɛɛlɛ e à gɛ̀ bↄ̀a.  
\v 18 Dii to Lua wɛ̃nadↄ̃ɛ̀ yã́kpalɛkɛgↄↄzĩ. Ń dↄnlɛ zↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ a kɛ̀mɛɛ Ɛfɛsɛ dↄ̃ sã́asã. 
\c 2  
\s1 Kilisi Yesu zĩgↄ̃ maa 
\p  
\v 1 Mpi sↄ̃ ma nɛ́, ǹyↄ̃ gbãa ń gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ Lua vĩwanↄ naa Kilisi Yesuwao.  
\v 2 Yã́ pↄ́ ń mà má ò dasi wáa na gbɛ̃́ náaide pↄ́ aa fↄ̃ da gbɛ̃pãleↄnɛↄ ↄzĩ.  
\v 3 Taasikɛmanↄ Kilisi Yesu zĩgↄ̃ maa ũ.  
\v 4 Dṹnia yã́ lí dↄaa zĩgↄ̃ pↄ́ kú zĩlauɛo, kɛ́ aà yã́ e ka a diigu yã́i.  
\v 5 Bakpaaĩna sↄ̃, tó i bàalɛ a zɛ́wao, a fùa eo.\f + \fr 2.5 \ft 1Kln 9.24-27\f* 
\v 6 Zↄ̃ɛ pↄ́ zĩ gbãa kɛ̀ mɛ́ ì a baa sɛ́ sɛ̃́ia.  
\v 7 Làasookɛ yã́ pↄ́ má òpiↄwa, asa Dii a ń gba ↄ̃nↄ apii guu. 
\p  
\v 8 To Davidi bui Yesu Kilisi pↄ́ bↄ̀ gau yã́ àↄ dↄngu. Baona pↄ́ mi kpan we.  
\v 9 A yã́i málɛ taasikɛi. Wà mↄkàa lán dàakɛnawa, ãma wa fↄ̃ mↄka Lua yã́wao.  
\v 10 Ayãmɛto mi yã́pii fↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua ń sɛ́ↄ yã́i, kɛ́ ampiↄ sↄ̃, Lua ń suaba, aai gawi pↄ́ lí láao e naa Kilisi Yesuwa.  
\v 11 Yã́ɛ bee sĩana vĩ: 
\q1 Tó wa gaaànↄ, wáↄ kuaànↄ.\f + \fr 2.11 \ft Lom 6.8\f* 
\q1  
\v 12 Tó wa mɛnafↄ̃̀, wáↄ kibleaànↄ. 
\q1 Tó wa lelekpàaàzi, 
\q1 aàpi a kpáwázi sↄ̃ɛ.\f + \fr 2.12 \ft Mat 10.33\f* 
\q1  
\v 13 Tó wá náai vĩo, ìↄ náai vĩɛ, 
\q1 asa a we lelekpa azĩaio. 
\s1 Dii zĩkɛna maa ń lɛkpaaoo 
\p  
\v 14 Yã́piↄ dↄ n gbɛ̃́ↄgu, ní nanɛ́ Luazi aasu lɛkpaa pã kɛ Lua yã́ musuo. A ài vĩo, ì gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ maↄ ↄ̃̀ↄkpaɛ.  
\v 15 Ãiakɛ, kɛ́ Lua e n sáaukpa, zĩkɛna pↄ́ ì yã́ sĩande polonɛ́ wásawasa, wí lí aà kũ aà zĩ yã́ musuo ũ.  
\v 16 Ɛ̃ yãbↄlɛa pã pↄ́ lí kpaaĩ ń Lua yã́ooɛ. Ì gbɛ̃́ↄ luayãdasai kã́fĩnɛ́ɛ,  
\v 17 ↄ̃ yã́ pↄ́ aaì danɛ́ ì ↄtamá lán sã́nɛwa. Imɛnɛ ń Filɛtio kú ń guu.  
\v 18 Aa kɛ̃̀ sĩanawa, aaì mɛ wà bↄ̀ gau kↄ̀, aaì gbɛ̃eↄ luanaaikɛa ↄ̃̀ↄkpaonɛ́.  
\v 19 Gia ń beeo ɛ̃ pↄ́ Lua dàalɛ zɛa gbãa, wà yã́ɛ bee kɛ̃̀wà: Dii gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ a pↄ́ ũↄ dↄ̃.\f + \fr 2.19 \ft Nao 16.5\f* Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì Dii sísi kɛ̃́ yãvãiwa. 
\p  
\v 20 Uada ìↄ pↄ́ↄ vĩ dasi. Wà a keeↄ kɛ̀ ń vuao ń ã́nusuo yã́gbiakɛbↄ ũ, mɛ́ wà a keeↄ kɛ̀ ń lío ń gĩo yãyↄↄnakɛbↄ ũ.  
\v 21 Tó gbɛ̃́ ↄbↄ̀lɛ yã́ bɛɛɛsai guu, a gↄ̃ yã́gbiakɛbↄ ũ, Dii zĩkɛbↄ maa ũ, iↄ ku maakɛa píi sↄu guu.  
\v 22 Bàalɛ ɛ̀waaso pↄnidɛaↄnɛ, ní tó maakɛa ń luanaaikɛao ń yea gbɛ̃́ↄzio ń kua ń kↄ̃o na dↄaanɛ sãnu ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaì Dii sísi ń nↄ̀sɛpuaoↄ.  
\v 23 Ɔbↄlɛ yã́ mìsai gwaa ń kↄ̃o guu. A dↄ̃a vĩo, mɛ́ ń dↄ̃ kɛ́ ì lɛkpaa inɛ́.  
\v 24 A maa Dii zↄ̀blena aàↄ lɛkpaa vĩo. Aàↄ busaa gbɛ̃́piiɛ, yãdanɛde maa pↄ́ ì gbɛ̃́ fↄ̃́ ũ,  
\v 25 i gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ a yã́ sioↄ gba laai busɛbusɛ. Wìliↄ dↄ̃o Lua a ń gba nↄ̀sɛlilɛa zɛ́, aai sĩana dↄ̃,  
\v 26 aai pili Ibiisi pↄ́ ń kṹ ń a bao à ń dá a pↄeã guuwa, aai su ń laaiwa. 
\c 3  
\s1 Gbɛ̃nazĩnaↄ yãkɛa gↄↄgbɛzãzĩ 
\p  
\v 1 Ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ kɛ́ gↄↄ gbɛzãɛ beeↄ aaↄ zĩ'ũ.  
\v 2 Gbɛ̃́ↄ zĩa yã́ a dↄaanɛ́, ↄ̃a a ń sↄ̃ ble. Aaↄ dɛ waladeↄ ũ, ĩ́andãnaↄ, gbɛ̃sↄ̃sↄ̃naↄ, de ń dao yãmansaiↄ, guluↄ, luayãdansaiↄ,  
\v 3 nↄ̀sɛsaideↄ, awamansaiↄ, gbɛ̃́ tↄbɛ̃ɛsinaↄ, faasaideↄ, ãiapãsĩdeↄ, maa ibɛɛↄ,  
\v 4 bↄnkpɛdeↄ, làasoosaideↄ ń yↄ̃̀ↄdeↄ. Aaↄ ye pↄnakɛai dɛ Lua yã́la.  
\v 5 Aaì lousisi, ãma an yã́ lí kↄ̃sɛ ń Lua gbãaoo. Kɛ̃́ gbɛ̃́piↄwa.  
\v 6 Gbɛ̃́ bee taaↄ ì gɛ̃ nↄɛ pↄ́ lí mi gbãɛoↄzi, aai ikokɛmá. Duuna sadà nↄɛpiↄgu, dↄ́ɛ'ĩi mɛ́ gↄ̃̀nɛ́,  
\v 7 aaìↄ yãdada gↄↄpii, ãma aali sĩana dↄ̃o.  
\v 8 Lá Zanɛsi ń Zãblɛsio bↄ̀ Mↄizi kpɛ,\f + \fr 3.8 \ft Bↄa 7.11-12\f* màa gbɛ̃́piↄ ì bↄ sĩana kpɛ. An làasoo kolea, mɛ́ luanaaikɛn gianaↄnɛ.  
\v 9 Aa gɛa'aɛ vĩ lↄo, asa gbɛ̃́pii ń mìsaikɛ dↄ̃, lá wà Zanɛsi ń Zãblɛsio pↄ́ dↄ̃̀wa. 
\s1 Lua yã́ ài 
\p  
\v 10 Mpi sↄ̃ ń tɛmazi, ń ma kua dↄ̃ ń ma yãdanɛo ń yã́ pↄ́ málɛ yáo ń ma luanaaikɛao ń ma mɛnakɛao ń ma yea gbɛ̃́ↄzio ń ma zɛa gbãao  
\v 11 ń ĩa pↄ́ wa dàao ń taasi pↄ́ má kɛ̀o. Ń yã́ pↄ́ ma le Antiↄsi ń Ikↄniuo ń Lisitao dↄ̃\f + \fr 3.11 \ft Zĩn 13.50, 14.5, 19\f* ń ĩa zↄ̃ↄ daaa pↄ́ má fↄ̃̀o. Dii ma bↄ apii guu.\f + \fr 3.11 \ft Soũ 34.19\f* 
\v 12 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa ye wàↄ ku luayãmanaↄ ũ naa Kilisi Yesuwaↄ gí wɛ́tɛ̃a eio.  
\v 13 Gbɛ̃vãiↄ ń kↄ̃nideↄ, an vãi aↄ gbãbↄbↄɛ, aai gbɛ̃́ↄ sã́sã, ampiↄ sↄ̃ aaↄ sã́sãaɛ.  
\v 14 Mpi sↄ̃, zɛ ń yã́ pↄ́ ń dàda ń sì sĩana ũo. Ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dàdanɛ́ↄ dↄ̃,  
\v 15 asa ń Luayãtaala dↄ̃ za n nɛ́zĩ. A fↄ̃ n gba ↄ̃nↄ, i n ka Kilisi Yesu náaikɛa pↄ́ ì ń suabawa.  
\v 16 Yã́ pↄ́ kú lápiↄ guu bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́i píiɛ. A ài vĩ, asa ì sĩana danɛ́, ì ń ɛɛkanɛ́ ń ↄzĩ, ì ń gba laai, ì lɛdamá yãkɛa a zɛ́wa musu,  
\v 17 kɛ́ Lua gbɛ̃́ e àↄ wásawasa kua maakɛa píi sↄu guu. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Ma nanɛ Lua ń Kilisi Yesuozi aà ɛa mↄa kpalablei ń aà yã́kpalɛkɛa ń gbɛ̃́ bɛ̃́ɛↄ ń gyaadeↄ yã́i,  
\v 2 Lua yã́ waasokɛ, à zɛkɛ̀ i zɛkɛo, wɛtã. Ǹ ń lele, ǹ ń gba laai, naɛmá, ní yãdanɛ́ ń mɛna zↄ̃ↄo.  
\v 3 Asa gↄↄe a mↄ kɛ́ gbɛ̃́ↄ we swã́sɛ yã́ sĩandeio. Aa yãdanɛdeↄ kãaańzi ńzĩa pↄeãwaɛ, aa yã́ pↄ́ káńgu danɛ́.  
\v 4 Aa gi sĩanai, aai zɛ ń fĩↄ.  
\v 5 Mpi sↄ̃, ǹyↄ̃ laai vĩ yã́pii musu. Taasi fↄ̃́, ní baonakpanakɛa kɛ, ní n zĩ lɛpapa. 
\s1 Pↄlu kua ga lɛ́zĩ Loma 
\p  
\v 6 Ma gↄↄ pà kↄ̀, wa ma au tↄ̃́lɛ sa'o'i ũ tia.  
\v 7 Ma dɛ̃ɛ maa nɛ̀, ma bakpaaĩ pↄ́ Lua dìlɛ kɛ̀ ma bↄlɛi. Ma Yesu yã́ kũ̀ a zɛ́wa.  
\v 8 Kua maa fùa dilɛa, àlɛ ma dã sa. Dii Yã́kpalɛkɛn maa mɛ́ a kpamɛɛ yã́kpalɛkɛgↄↄzĩ. I kɛ mámɛ má adoo, ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ye aà mↄaiↄ píiɛ. 
\p  
\v 9 Zɛwɛɛlɛ mↄ́ ma kĩ́i kpakpa.  
\v 10 Demasi ma to we à tà Tɛsaloni, kɛ́ a ye dṹniai yã́i. Kɛlɛsã tà Galati bùsuu, mɛ́ Titu tà Dalamati bùsuu.  
\v 11 Luku mɛ́ gↄ̃̀manↄ ado. Maaku sɛ à mↄ sãnu, asa ì dↄmalɛ maamaaɛ.  
\v 12 Ma Tisiki gbàɛ Ɛfɛsɛ.  
\v 13 Tó ńlɛ mↄ́, ma ulatao pↄ́ má tò Kaapu bɛ Toloasi\f + \fr 4.13 \ft Zĩn 20.6\f* sɛ́, ní mↄomɛɛ ń ma láↄ, atɛ̃sa a pↄ́ pↄ́ wa kɛ̀ ń báaoↄ. 
\p  
\v 14 Alɛsãnda sia yãvãikɛ̀mɛɛ maamaaɛ. Dii a yã́ pↄ́ a kɛ̀pi fĩaboɛ̀.\f + \fr 4.14 \ft Soũ 62.13\f* 
\v 15 Laaikaaàzi, asa à bↄ̀ wá yã́ kpɛ pãsĩpãsĩɛ.  
\v 16 Yã́kpalɛkɛamanↄ sɛ̃́ia guu gbɛ̃e i zɛmanↄo. Wà ma to we píiɛ. Lua su ń yã́pi dao.  
\v 17 Dii zɛ̀manↄ à ma gba gbãa, ↄ̃ ma zɛ'è ma baonakpà wásawasa, buipãleↄ mà píi. À ma bↄ nↄ̀ↄmusu lɛ́zĩ.  
\v 18 Dii a ma bↄ yãvãi guu píi, a ma suaba e ma gɛ kaò aà kpalau musu. Ɔ̃mɛ gawi vĩ gↄↄpii, ãmi. 
\p  
\v 19 Fↄkpa Pisii ń Akilasiowa ń Ɔnɛsifↄↄ bɛdeↄ.\f + \fr 4.19 \ft 2Tim 1.16-17\f* 
\v 20 Elasa gↄ̃̀ Kↄlɛni. Ma Tↄfiũ tò ń gyão Milɛti.  
\v 21 Zɛwɛɛlɛ mↄ́ e buziɛ àↄ ká. Ebulu ń Pudɛo ń Linuo ń Kolodiao ń wá gbɛ̃́ↄ píi fↄkpàma.  
\v 22 Dii àↄ kunnↄ, i gbɛ̃kɛkɛɛ́ ápii.